snippet.textDisplay: My eyelids sometimes get SO DRY in the winter that they PEEL! The best thing I’ve found to treat it is cheap, simple, and effective. I create a 50/50 mix of vitamin E oil and jojoba oil and pipe it into a glass rollerball container. I put it all over my eyes and massage it into my eyebrows and eyelashes. It is nourishing and seems to help my eyelashes grow and my brows thicken.
